ce","orange peel","orange tree","orange slice"],"synonyms_en":["amber","tangerine","citrus hue"],"example_sentence":"I bought an orange for breakfast.","example_es":"Compré una naranja para el desayuno.","example_en":"I bought an orange for breakfast.","mnemonic_en":"Picture a bright orange fruit shouting Naranja at the market.","cloze_distractors_en":[],"examples":[{"es":"Compré una naranja para el desayuno.","en":"I bought an orange for breakfast."}]},{"spanish_text":"Rosa","english_text":"Pink","section_name":"English Basics","part_of_speech":"adjective","definition_en":"A pale red color.","main_translations_es":["flor","color rosado","rosa (nombre propio)"],"collocations":["in the pink","pink slip","pink noise","pink flamingo"],"synonyms_en":["rosy","blush","magenta"],"example_sentence":"I like the pink shirt.","example_es":"Me gusta la camisa rosa.","example_en":"I like the pink shirt.","mnemonic_en":"Imagine a pink rose, a bright rosa, blooming to remind you pink.","cloze_distractors_en":[],"examples":[{"es":"Me gusta la camisa rosa.","en":"I like the pink shirt."}]},{"spanish_text":"Marrón","english_text":"Brown","section_name":"English Basics","part_of_speech":"adjective","definition_en":"A dark orange‑red color resembling chocolate or earth.","main_translations_es":["café","pardo","castaño"],"collocations":["brown sugar","brown eyes","brown bear","brown paper"],"synonyms_en":["tan","chocolate","umber"],"example_sentence":"I bought a brown jacket for the fall.","example_es":"Compré una chaqueta marrón para el otoño.","example_en":"I bought a brown jacket for the fall.","mnemonic_en":"Imagine a brown bear wearing a maroon (marrón) scarf.","cloze_distractors_en":[],"examples":[{"es":"Compré una chaqueta marrón para el otoño.","en":"I bought a brown jacket for the fall."}]},{"spanish_text":"Gris","english_text":"Gray","section_name":"English Basics","part_of_speech":"adjective","definition_en":"A neutral color that lies between black and white.","main_translati