t the glass on the table.","mnemonic_en":"Picture a clear glass that looks just like a Spanish vaso on the table","cloze_distractors_en":[],"examples":[{"es":"Pon el vaso sobre la mesa.","en":"Put the glass on the table."}]},{"spanish_text":"Plato","english_text":"Plate","section_name":"Cafe Counter Basics","part_of_speech":"noun","definition_en":"A flat dish used for serving or eating food.","main_translations_es":["plato","cazuela","plato hondo"],"collocations":["plate of food","clean your plate","plate tectonics"],"synonyms_en":["dish","platter","serving dish"],"example_sentence":"I placed the plate on the table.","example_es":"Puse el plato sobre la mesa.","example_en":"I placed the plate on the table.","mnemonic_en":"Picture Plato serving ideas on a shining plate","cloze_distractors_en":[],"examples":[{"es":"Puse el plato sobre la mesa.","en":"I placed the plate on the table."}]},{"spanish_text":"Cuchara","english_text":"Spoon","section_name":"Cafe Counter Basics","part_of_speech":"noun","definition_en":"A utensil with a shallow bowl and a handle used for scooping, stirring, or serving food.","main_translations_es":["cucharita","cucharilla","cuchara de té"],"collocations":["spoonful of sugar","spoon feeding","spoon and fork","spoon in the drawer"],"synonyms_en":["ladle","dipper","spoonful"],"example_sentence":"I need a spoon to stir the soup.","example_es":"Necesito una cuchara para mezclar la sopa.","example_en":"I need a spoon to stir the soup.","mnemonic_en":"Picture a shiny spoon acting as a tiny Cuchara scooping soup.","cloze_distractors_en":[],"examples":[{"es":"Necesito una cuchara para mezclar la sopa.","en":"I need a spoon to stir the soup."}]},{"spanish_text":"Tenedor","english_text":"Fork","section_name":"Cafe Counter Basics","part_of_speech":"noun","definition_en":"A utensil with two or more prongs used for eating or serving food.","main_translations_es":["tenedor","tenedor de mesa","tenedor de cocina"],"collocations":["fork in the road","fork out",