ns an old research file","cloze_distractors_en":[],"examples":[{"es":"La investigación previa sugiere que el método es efectivo.","en":"Previous research suggests that the method is effective."}]},{"spanish_text":"Cuerpo de evidencia","english_text":"Body of evidence","section_name":"Academic English","part_of_speech":"noun phrase","definition_en":"A collection of facts, testimony, or other information that together support a particular conclusion or argument.","main_translations_es":["Conjunto de pruebas","Cuerpo probatorio","Colección de evidencia"],"collocations":["a substantial body of evidence","the body of evidence suggests","the body of evidence points to","the body of evidence is compelling"],"synonyms_en":["evidence base","proof corpus","supporting material"],"example_sentence":"The body of evidence presented at the trial was sufficient to convict the defendant.","example_es":"El cuerpo de evidencia presentado en el juicio fue suficiente para condenar al acusado.","example_en":"The body of evidence presented at the trial was sufficient to convict the defendant.","mnemonic_en":"Visualize a cuerpo (body) stacked with piles of evidence.","cloze_distractors_en":[],"examples":[{"es":"El cuerpo de evidencia presentado en el juicio fue suficiente para condenar al acusado.","en":"The body of evidence presented at the trial was sufficient to convict the defendant."}]},{"spanish_text":"Conjunto de datos","english_text":"Dataset","section_name":"Academic English","part_of_speech":"noun","definition_en":"A collection of data, typically organized for analysis or reference.","main_translations_es":["Conjunto de datos","Base de datos","Colección de datos"],"collocations":["large dataset","training dataset","public dataset","dataset analysis"],"synonyms_en":["data collection","data bank","data repository"],"example_sentence":"The dataset contains information about household energy consumption.","example_es":"El conjunto de datos contiene información sobre el consumo energé