ess data before generating the report.","example_es":"Necesitamos procesar datos antes de generar el informe.","example_en":"We need to process data before generating the report.","mnemonic_en":"Picture a processor blending raw numbers like a kitchen blender, turning data into smooth info.","cloze_distractors_en":[],"examples":[{"es":"Necesitamos procesar datos antes de generar el informe.","en":"We need to process data before generating the report."}]},{"spanish_text":"Respaldado por evidencia","english_text":"Evidence-based","section_name":"Academic English","part_of_speech":"adjective","definition_en":"Based on or derived from evidence.","main_translations_es":["Basado en evidencia","Fundamentado en evidencia","Sustentado por evidencia"],"collocations":["evidence-based practice","evidence-based approach","evidence-based medicine","evidence-based policy"],"synonyms_en":["empirically supported","data-driven","research-backed"],"example_sentence":"The new treatment is evidence-based, relying on scientific data.","example_es":"El nuevo tratamiento está respaldado por evidencia científica.","example_en":"The new treatment is evidence-based, relying on scientific data.","mnemonic_en":"Picture a sturdy back supporting piles of evidence like a bookshelf.","cloze_distractors_en":[],"examples":[{"es":"El nuevo tratamiento está respaldado por evidencia científica.","en":"The new treatment is evidence-based, relying on scientific data."}]},{"spanish_text":"Sustancial","english_text":"Substantial","section_name":"Academic English","part_of_speech":"adjective","definition_en":"Considerable in amount, size, or importance; significant.","main_translations_es":["significativo","considerable","importante"],"collocations":["substantial amount","substantial evidence","substantial increase","substantial impact"],"synonyms_en":["considerable","significant","sizeable"],"example_sentence":"The increase in investment was substantial this year.","example_es":"El aumento de la inversión fu