o para la investigación.","en":"This finding is significant for the research."}]},{"spanish_text":"Insignificante","english_text":"Negligible","section_name":"Academic English","part_of_speech":"adjective","definition_en":"so small or unimportant that it is not worth considering","main_translations_es":["Irrelevante","Trivial","Mínimo"],"collocations":["negligible amount","negligible impact","negligible risk","negligible difference"],"synonyms_en":["insignificant","trivial","minor"],"example_sentence":"The impact of that mistake is negligible on the final result.","example_es":"El impacto de ese error es insignificante en el resultado final.","example_en":"The impact of that mistake is negligible on the final result.","mnemonic_en":"Picture a negligible speck of dust that the word insignificant (insignificante) can’t even notice.","cloze_distractors_en":[],"examples":[{"es":"El impacto de ese error es insignificante en el resultado final.","en":"The impact of that mistake is negligible on the final result."}]},{"spanish_text":"Rigurosidad","english_text":"Rigor","section_name":"Academic English","part_of_speech":"noun","definition_en":"strictness or exactness in standards, procedures, or analysis","main_translations_es":["rigor","exigencia","meticulosidad"],"collocations":["academic rigor","rigor of the test","rigor in methodology","rigor and precision"],"synonyms_en":["strictness","severity","exactness"],"example_sentence":"The rigor of the scientific method ensures reliable results.","example_es":"La rigurosidad del método científico garantiza resultados confiables.","example_en":"The rigor of the scientific method ensures reliable results.","mnemonic_en":"Imagine a strict ruler measuring with rigor, echoing the Spanish riguroso in every precise line.","cloze_distractors_en":[],"examples":[{"es":"La rigurosidad del método científico garantiza resultados confiables.","en":"The rigor of the scientific method ensures reliable results."}]},{"spanish_text":"Coherencia"