 trusted to provide accurate and trustworthy information.","main_translations_es":["Fuente confiable","Fuente segura","Fuente fidedigna"],"collocations":["according to reliable sources","a reliable source of information","from a reliable source","reliable source of news"],"synonyms_en":["trustworthy source","dependable source","authoritative source"],"example_sentence":"This article is a reliable source for studying history.","example_es":"Este artículo es una fuente fiable para estudiar la historia.","example_en":"This article is a reliable source for studying history.","mnemonic_en":"A reliable source is like a steady fountain (fuente) that never stops flowing truth.","cloze_distractors_en":[],"examples":[{"es":"Este artículo es una fuente fiable para estudiar la historia.","en":"This article is a reliable source for studying history."}]},{"spanish_text":"Desinformación","english_text":"Misinformation","section_name":"News and Society","part_of_speech":"noun","definition_en":"False or inaccurate information that is spread deliberately or unintentionally.","main_translations_es":["Información errónea","Noticias falsas","Información falsa"],"collocations":["spread misinformation","combat misinformation","misinformation campaign","misinformation about"],"synonyms_en":["false information","disinformation","fake news"],"example_sentence":"Misinformation about the vaccine is causing fear.","example_es":"La desinformación sobre la vacuna está generando miedo.","example_en":"Misinformation about the vaccine is causing fear.","mnemonic_en":"Picture a missed info sign exploding, spreading desinformación everywhere.","cloze_distractors_en":[],"examples":[{"es":"La desinformación sobre la vacuna está generando miedo.","en":"Misinformation about the vaccine is causing fear."}]},{"spanish_text":"Información falsa","english_text":"False information","section_name":"News and Society","part_of_speech":"noun","definition_en":"Information that is incorrect or misleading.","main_tran